BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 23) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (So remember: you are not supposed to be like everyone else.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Maybe you're quiet in a world of loud people. Maybe you're slow in a world of fast ones.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Maybe you're different in ways that feel awkward or strange.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (But those differences? They're your superpowers. Your shell. Your unique gift to the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (world.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Don't wish them away. Discover why they're wonderful. Because they ARE wonderful.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (And so are you. Exactly as you are. Wings or no wings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A beautiful final image of the Emerald Valley with all the different) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (animals   tortoises, birds, fish, rabbits   each doing what they do best, a celebration of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (diversity and being yourself]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
