BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 24) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Here is something to try, dear reader:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Instead of thinking about what you wish you could do, make a list of what you CAN do.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Write down five things that make you YOU. Five things you are good at. Five things that) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (make you different from everyone else.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (Maybe you are patient. Maybe you are creative. Maybe you are strong, or kind, or funny, or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (observant.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Those are not just traits. Those are your superpowers. Your shell. Wear them proudly.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A child writing a list of their own unique qualities and strengths, each) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (one drawn as a shield or superpower emblem, celebrating their unique traits]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
