stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And whenever you catch yourself wishing you were someone else   stop.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Instead, ask: 'What can I do today that only I can do? What makes me special that I have) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (not even discovered yet?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (The answers might surprise you. Because you, dear reader, are wonderfully and uniquely) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (made.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (There is no one else in the whole world exactly like you. And the world needs exactly what) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (only YOU can give.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (So be yourself. Fully. Proudly. Beautifully. Just like Taro learned to be.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A child looking at their own reflection in a pond with a smile, seeing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (their unique self clearly for the first time, accepting and loving who they are, sunshine) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (and flowers around them]) Tj ET
endstream
