stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Appreciate What Makes You Unique) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Taro learned that wishing to be someone else means losing what makes YOU special. His) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (shell, his slowness, his weight   all the things he thought were weaknesses   turned out) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (to be incredible strengths. The same is true for you! The things that make you different) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (are not flaws. They are features. They are gifts. They are exactly what the world needs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (Instead of wishing you were like someone else, discover the superpower hiding in what) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.4 Td (makes you, you.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
