stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Discussion Questions for Parents) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. What's something about yourself that you sometimes wish was different? Can you think of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (how it might actually be a strength?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (2. Why do you think Taro missed his shell after only two days without it?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (3. What are some things that tortoises can do that birds can't? What can birds do that) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.8 Td (tortoises can't?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 557.0 Td (4. Is it bad to admire what other people can do? What's the difference between admiring) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 543.0 Td (others and wishing you were them?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 519.2 Td (5. What makes YOU unique? What can you do that nobody else does quite the same way?) Tj ET
endstream
